sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User Browser
    participant Router as OpenShift Router<br/>HAProxy<br/>443/TCP TLS 1.2+
    participant OAuthProxy as oauth-proxy sidecar<br/>Head Pod<br/>8443/TCP TLS
    participant Dashboard as Ray Dashboard<br/>Head Pod<br/>8265/TCP HTTP
    participant Operator as CodeFlare Operator<br/>controller-runtime
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP TLS 1.2+
    participant InitCert as Init Container<br/>(create-cert)
    participant HeadNode as Ray Head Node<br/>10001/TCP gRPC
    participant WorkerNode as Ray Worker Nodes<br/>10001/TCP gRPC
    participant RayClient as Ray Client

    Note over User, Dashboard: Flow 1: Ray Dashboard Access (OpenShift)
    User->>Router: GET /dashboard<br/>HTTPS/443<br/>TLS 1.2+
    Router->>OAuthProxy: Forward (TLS Reencrypt)<br/>HTTPS/8443<br/>OpenShift OAuth Token
    OAuthProxy->>Dashboard: Proxy after auth<br/>HTTP/8265 (localhost)<br/>No auth (proxied)
    Dashboard-->>OAuthProxy: Dashboard HTML
    OAuthProxy-->>Router: Response (TLS)
    Router-->>User: Dashboard Response

    Note over Operator, InitCert: Flow 2: RayCluster mTLS Certificate Generation
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Watch RayCluster CRs<br/>HTTPS/443<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: RayCluster Event
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create CA Secret<br/>(RSA 2048-bit, 1yr validity)<br/>HTTPS/443
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: Secret Created
    Note over InitCert: Init container mounts<br/>CA cert from Secret
    InitCert->>InitCert: Generate per-pod TLS cert<br/>signed by cluster CA<br/>SANs: localhost, pod IP,<br/>route hostname, head FQDN
    Note over InitCert: Writes to<br/>/home/ray/workspace/tls

    Note over RayClient, WorkerNode: Flow 3: Ray Client Connection (OpenShift)
    RayClient->>Router: Connect<br/>HTTPS/443<br/>TLS Passthrough<br/>mTLS Client Cert
    Router->>HeadNode: Forward (Passthrough)<br/>gRPC/10001<br/>mTLS (cluster CA)
    HeadNode->>WorkerNode: Distribute work<br/>gRPC/10001<br/>mTLS (cluster CA)<br/>RAY_USE_TLS=1
    WorkerNode-->>HeadNode: Results
    HeadNode-->>Router: Response
    Router-->>RayClient: Results
